# 🚀tkintertools🚀

<img src="tkt.png" style="height: 128px" alt="Logo" />

`tkintertools` 是 Python3 内置模块 `tkinter` 的一个辅助开发模块\
The `tkintertools` is an auxiliary development module of the Python3 built-in module `tkinter`

